snippet.title: Valkyria Chronicles 3 - A Clash Battle? Edy vs. Dahau [Extra Episode] [DLC]
snippet.description:
Valkyria Chronicles 3
Edy detachment's Story:
A Clash Battle? Edy vs. Dahau
July 1935
Mission: "Withdrawal of the Edy Detachment"
Objective: Edy reaches designated point
Difficulty: ---
Weapon received: VB sch35 (mauler)

Meanwhile somewhere else in Gallia... Edy and her squadmates are dealing with the rest of the Calamity Raven.

If there are Susie fans out there I'm very sorry, but I couldn't avoid her fate (twice).
